                <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>; grapes, early, <supplied reason="lost">under guarantee, so much</supplied>; without guar<supplied reason="lost">antee, so much; grapes, black 
                    under guarantee</supplied>, 5 drachmas; without <supplied reason="lost">guarantee, so much</supplied>; <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">figs, so much; raisin</supplied>, 3 drachmas;  hay, <supplied reason="lost">cultivated
                    per cartload, so much; selvatico, per</supplied> cartload, (at least) 4 drachmas; <supplied reason="lost">straw, per net, so much</supplied>; <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">olives, so much; oil, 10</supplied> drachmas; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.                  
